trans-unit.source: Defines a means for an <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner" /> to return its designer verbs.
trans-unit.target: 定義 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner" /> 傳回其設計工具動詞的方法。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner" /> for which to return the activity verb collection.
trans-unit.target: 要為其傳回活動動詞集合的 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner" />。

trans-unit.source: Returns the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerVerb" /> collection associated with the specified <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner" />.
trans-unit.target: 傳回 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerVerb" /> 集合，這個集合與指定的 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner" /> 關聯。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerVerbCollection" /> that contains the verbs associated with the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesignerVerbCollection" />，其中包含與 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner" /> 關聯的動詞。
